		<title><![CDATA[Sample Page]]></title>
		<link>https://stoneacre.anvil-designs.co.uk/sample-page/</link>
		<pubDate>Sun, 06 Jun 2021 18:50:38 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://stoneacre.anvil-designs.co.uk/?page_id=2</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p>Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)</p></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>...or something like this:</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:quote -->
<blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</p></blockquote>
<!-- /wp:quote -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="https://stoneacre.anvil-designs.co.uk/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Privacy Policy]]></title>
		<link>https://stoneacre.anvil-designs.co.uk/privacy-policy/</link>
		<pubDate>Sun, 06 Jun 2021 18:50:38 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://stoneacre.anvil-designs.co.uk/?page_id=3</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:heading --><h2>Who we are</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>Our website address is: https://stoneacre.anvil-designs.co.uk.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>Comments</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>When visitors leave comments on the site we collect the data shown in the comments form, and also the visitor&#8217;s IP address and browser user agent string to help spam detection.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>An anonymized string created from your email address (also called a hash) may be provided to the Gravatar service to see if you are using it. The Gravatar service privacy policy is available here: https://automattic.com/privacy/. After approval of your comment, your profile picture is visible to the public in the context of your comment.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>Media</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>If you upload images to the website, you should avoid uploading images with embedded location data (EXIF GPS) included. Visitors to the website can download and extract any location data from images on the website.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>Cookies</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>If you leave a comment on our site you may opt-in to saving your name, email address and website in cookies. These are for your convenience so that you do not have to fill in your details again when you leave another comment. These cookies will last for one year.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>If you visit our login page, we will set a temporary cookie to determine if your browser accepts cookies. This cookie contains no personal data and is discarded when you close your browser.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>When you log in, we will also set up several cookies to save your login information and your screen display choices. Login cookies last for two days, and screen options cookies last for a year. If you select &quot;Remember Me&quot;, your login will persist for two weeks. If you log out of your account, the login cookies will be removed.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>If you edit or publish an article, an additional cookie will be saved in your browser. This cookie includes no personal data and simply indicates the post ID of the article you just edited. It expires after 1 day.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>Embedded content from other websites</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>Articles on this site may include embedded content (e.g. videos, images, articles, etc.). Embedded content from other websites behaves in the exact same way as if the visitor has visited the other website.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>These websites may collect data about you, use cookies, embed additional third-party tracking, and monitor your interaction with that embedded content, including tracking your interaction with the embedded content if you have an account and are logged in to that website.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>Who we share your data with</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>If you request a password reset, your IP address will be included in the reset email.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>How long we retain your data</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>If you leave a comment, the comment and its metadata are retained indefinitely. This is so we can recognize and approve any follow-up comments automatically instead of holding them in a moderation queue.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p>For users that register on our website (if any), we also store the personal information they provide in their user profile. All users can see, edit, or delete their personal information at any time (except they cannot change their username). Website administrators can also see and edit that information.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>What rights you have over your data</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>If you have an account on this site, or have left comments, you can request to receive an exported file of the personal data we hold about you, including any data you have provided to us. You can also request that we erase any personal data we hold about you. This does not include any data we are obliged to keep for administrative, legal, or security purposes.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:heading --><h2>Where we send your data</h2><!-- /wp:heading --><!-- wp:paragraph --><p><strong class="privacy-policy-tutorial">Suggested text: </strong>Visitor comments may be checked through an automated spam detection service.</p><!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>

</strong></h1>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" text_font_size="18px" text_letter_spacing="2px" custom_margin="||50px|||" custom_padding="34px|||32px||"]<p class="v1MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #ffffff;">State-of-the-art machinery and technology guarantee maximum efficiency and </span><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #ffffff;">the utmost precision. <p class="v1MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #ffffff;"></span></p>
<p class="v1MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: #ffffff;"></span></p>
<p class="v1MsoNormal" style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: #ffffff;"><a href="about-hobby" style="color: #ffffff;"><span style="font-size: 14.0pt;">Read More...</span></a></span></p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_tabs active_tab_background_color="#41A02D" inactive_tab_background_color="#f4f4f4" active_tab_text_color="#FFFFFF" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" tab_font_size="16px" tab_letter_spacing="2px" tab_line_height="2.7em" overflow-y="auto" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"][et_pb_tab title="About Stoneacre" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"]<p style="text-align: center;">Found in over 100 locations in England and Wales, Stoneacre Motor Group is one of the fastest-growing franchise dealership groups in the UK.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Representing multiple world renown brands, our <a href="https://www.stoneacre.co.uk/new-cars" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" draggable="false"><strong><u>New Car</u></strong></a> offering is comprehensive, with literally hundreds of cars to choose from.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">In our <a href="https://www.stoneacre.co.uk/used-cars" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" draggable="false"><strong><u>Used Car</u></strong></a> stock, the choice is even larger, with thousands of cars and vans in stock right now for you to drive away in.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Our <a href="https://www.stoneacre.co.uk/stoneacre-finance" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" draggable="false"><strong><u>finance options</u></strong></a> are many, and we always look to get our customers a deal that suits them and their budget.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">In addition, we have some of the best <a href="https://www.stoneacre.co.uk/service-and-aftersales" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" draggable="false"><strong><u>aftersales facilities</u></strong></a> in the country for your existing car to receive the care it needs.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Find your nearest <a href="https://www.stoneacre.co.uk/dealerships" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" draggable="false"><strong><u>Stoneacre dealership</u></strong></a> today and give us a visit.</p>[/et_pb_tab][et_pb_tab title="About Finance" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"]<p>Your content goes here. <p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">The compact OPTIMA ONTOUR EDITION is perfect for spontaneous city breaks and long, adventurous trips. Thanks to its compact dimensions (2.16 m in width), youll be able to negotiate narrow and bendy roads with confidence. The edition models come with a<br />wide range of equipment and are available with three layout options: a double<br />bed, island bed or single beds.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" custom_margin="-61px|||||" custom_padding="||0px|||"][et_pb_row column_structure="1_2,1_2" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" width="100%" custom_padding="0px||32px|||"][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"]<h2 class="v1MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Specs</strong></h2>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The design of the furniture in the top model range OPTIMA DE LUXE features straight lines, and the colours are perfectly coordinated. Scandinavian design combined with the Nordic concept of hygge makes your Hobby the most beautiful place in the world.</p>
<p>Whatever your needs, five layouts with up to five berths provide a luxurious experience. Choose between a double bed, single beds or a drop-down bed. A premium equipment package is always included, leaving nothing to be desired.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" custom_margin="||-1px||false|false" custom_padding="||||false|false" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_row column_structure="1_2,1_2" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" width="100%" custom_margin="|auto|-2px|auto||" custom_padding="0px||17px|||" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"]<h2 class="v1MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Specs</strong></h2>
<p class="v1MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"></p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.11" _module_preset="default" text_font_size="12px" global_colors_info="{}"]<table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 60px;" border="1">

<tr style="height: 10px;">
<td style="width: 50%; height: 10px;">
<p class="v1MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;">Category</p>

<td style="width: 50%; height: 10px;">Semi-integrated</td>
</tr>

<td style="width: 50%; height: 10px;">
<p class="v1MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;">Chassis cowl</p>
</td>
<td style="width: 50%; height: 10px;">Fiat</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 10px;">

<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The OPTIMA ONTOUR OVERCAB has everything you could ever want. Lots of space, large storage spaces, as well as modern and practical furnishings. The overcab serves as extra storage space during the day, and as an airy canopy bed at night.</p>
<p>Like all Hobby motorhomes, the Hobby OPTIMA ONTOUR OVERCAB also comes ready to hit the road thanks to the standard Hobby Complete ALL-INCLUSIVE package.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" custom_margin="-61px|||||" custom_padding="||0px|||" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_row column_structure="1_2,1_2" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" width="100%" custom_padding="0px||17px|||" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" global_colors_info="{}"]<h2 class="v1MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Specs</strong></h2>
<p class="v1MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"></p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.11" _module_preset="default" text_font_size="12px" hover_enabled="0" global_colors_info="{}" sticky_enabled="0"]<table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 60px;" border="1">

<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="v1MsoNormal">
<p>The Hobby VANTANA ONTOUR EDITION is perfect for you.</p>
<p>Our entry-level model has everything you could possibly need to travel in luxury. With a kitchen unit, stainless steel sink, double-burner hob and a 90-litre compressor refrigerator, the kitchen is perfectly equipped for mobile chefs. Comfy cold foam mattresses promise a restful nights sleep. The entire body is finished with B6 high-performance insulation and XPS foam to provide exceptional insulation. With a navigation and satellite system, including a TV, you also have the very best multimedia technology right from the get-go.</p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="v1MsoNormal">In addition to the luxurious HobbyComplete ALL-INCLUSIVE package, the Hobby VANTANA DE LUXE also boasts a 140 hp engine, 16-inch alloy rims and the extra-wide, panoramic roof vent HOBBY TOP.</p>
<p>The interior features a 90-litre, double-hinged, compressor refrigerator, which comes as standard and can be opened both ways, as well as pleasant ambient lighting. For its exterior design, you can choose between classic white and a variety of special paint finishes. The bumper is also painted in your chosen colour. For the upcoming season, the top model range will also be available with a choice of two furniture finishes.</p>

		<title><![CDATA[Terms and Conditions]]></title>
		<link>https://stoneacre.anvil-designs.co.uk/terms-and-conditions/</link>

		<content:encoded><![CDATA[[et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" background_color="#41A02D" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0" custom_padding="0px||0px|||"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" type="4_4"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"]<h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">Terms and Conditions</span></h1>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" type="4_4"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"]<section class="pagebuilder-container pagebuilder">
<section class="section-wrapper ">
<section class="section-wrapper-inner grid-x bgwhite block-card-container">
<section class="grid-x large-12 medium-12 small-12 grid-margin-x flex-child-auto content-block">
<section class="cell grid-x large-12 medium-12 small-12 flex-flip">
<section class="large-6 medium-12 small-12 copy flex-child-auto">
<div>
<h3><strong>IMPORTANT INFORMATION</strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>This Web site is operated by Decidebloom Ltd on behalf of its trading subsidiaries. Decidebloom Ltd is registered Company number - 3003995 | Registered office - Omega Boulevard, Capitol Park, Thorne, DN8 5TX | VAT Number - GB616996004</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>1. Accuracy and Contract</p>
<p>The information given is an invitation to treat and is given in good faith. If there are any characteristics you require, these can be given at the time of sale.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Any mileages quoted are approximate and may not be guaranteed - please confirm with the selling dealership before your purchase.</p>
<p>Specifications of models can change from time to time. We reserve the right to change the specifications of any of its products.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The information given is not intended to form the basis of any contract, and is merely an invitation to treat. Contracts can only be made by completing and signing an order form at the selling dealership and paying a deposit.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Any contract made with us is subject to our Standard Terms of Business. Copies are available at all of our dealerships and appear on all of our order forms and invoices or click here to view.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>2. Copyright</p>
<p>All materials and information on the site are the intellectual property of Decidebloom Ltd. The name Decidbloom and the logo, and that of other companies within the group are registered as service marks in the U.K.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>3. Jurisdiction and Law</p>
<p>This site is intended for the use of customers in the United Kingdom only. It was created and is operated according to the laws of England . Any disputes will be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the Courts of England and to the laws of England.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>4. Links</p>
<p>On this site you may be offered links to other sites operated by parties other than Decidebloom Ltd. The inclusion of any link to such sites does not imply endorsement by us of the sites or the services or products offered on such sites. We have not reviewed the sites which may be linked to this site and is not responsible for the content or accuracy of any off-site pages or any other sites linked.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>5. Severability</p>
<p>If any of these terms and conditions become or are declared to be illegal or otherwise unenforceable by any Court of competent jurisdiction such terms shall be deemed deleted (to the extent necessary) and all remaining terms shall remain in full force and effect.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>6. Limitation of Liability</p>
<p>Decidebloom Ltd excludes all liability (other than liability for death and personal injury) resulting from your access and use of the site.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>7. Data Protection</p>
<p>If you are taking out finance with your vehicle purchase the information you have provided for the finance proposal will be disclosed to lenders for the purposes of considering your credit application. Lenders may use this information to carry out searches with credit reference agencies. A record of those searches will be kept and may be used by other lenders in accessing applications from you and members of your household for credit in the future. Lenders will cross check this information with other lenders to help prevent fraud.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>8. Cookies Policy</p>
<p>A cookie is a small data file that is written to your hard drive, when you visit websites that use them. The file can hold information such as, a user ID that the site uses to track the pages you've visited, but the only personal information a cookie can hold is information you supply. It cant read data off your hard disk, or read cookie files created by other sites. Some parts of the Stoneacre websites use cookies to remember vehicles you have shortlisted. It does not correlate this information, with data about individual users, nor does it share this information or sell it to any third party.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>You do not need to have cookies turned on, to use any area of the Stoneacre websites. If you prefer not to receive them, you can set your browser to warn you before accepting them or to completely turn them off.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Any information collected about you will be used to firstly fulfil any service you might request and secondly improve how, as a company, we may be able to serve you and we will do this by making appropriate use of the information.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>The information you supply is stored in our database and used to improve customer service, marketing and communications. From time to time we may contact you with information about products and services we think may be of interest to you. We may share this information with other selected organisations. You have the right as an individual to find out what information we hold about you and to make corrections if necessary  you also have the right to ask us not to use the information supplied in a certain way.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>9. Distance Selling</p>
<p>If, and only if, the Customer has acted as a Consumer, where this Agreement has been completed away from our business premises and/or without any face to face contact between us and you; or anyone acting on your or our respective behalf, you may give notice to cancel this Agreement within 14 days without giving any reason.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>(a) This cancellation period will expire 14 days after the day on which you, or a third party on your behalf, takes delivery or otherwise acquires physical possession of the Goods. To exercise this right to cancel, you must inform us of your decision to cancel this Agreement in writing by clear statement (e.g. a letter sent by post, fax or email) to our address / email as set out on our order form. You may use the order cancellation form which can be found on our website if you wish.</p>
<p>(b) To meet the cancellation deadline, it is sufficient for you to send your communication confirming your exercise of the right to cancel before the cancellation period has expired.</p>
<p>(c) If you cancel this Agreement, we will reimburse to you all payments received from you under this Agreement, without undue delay, and not later than:-</p>
<p>i. 14 days after the day on which we receive the Goods back; or</p>
<p>ii. (if earlier) 14 days after the day you provide evidence that you have returned the Goods; or</p>
<p>iii. if there were no Goods supplied, 14 days after the day on which we are informed about your decision to cancel this agreement.</p>
<p>(d) We will make the reimbursement using the same means of payment as you have used for the initial transaction, unless you have expressly agreed otherwise, but in any event you will not incur any fees as a result of the reimbursement.</p>
<p>(e) We may withhold reimbursement until we have received the Goods back or you have sent evidence of having sent back the Goods to us, whichever is the earliest. You should send back the Goods or deliver them back to us at the address as shown on our order form, without undue delay and in any event not later than 14 days after the day on which you communicate your cancellation of this Agreement to us.</p>
<p>(f) This deadline is met if you send back the Goods before the period of 14 days has expired. We will require that you bear the cost of returning the Goods to us.</p>
<p>(g) You must take reasonable care of the Goods whilst they are in your possession. You will be responsible for any loss or damage from when they are delivered to you until when they are returned to us.</p>
<p>(h) You are liable for any diminished value of the Goods resulting from the handling other than what is necessary to establish the nature, characteristics and functioning of the Goods. For vehicle sales, a mileage charge of 40p per mile will also be charged over and above the mileage on the vehicle at the time of delivery.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>10. Call Recording &amp; Subject Access Request</p>
<p>Stoneacre monitor and record calls on certain lines for training purposes. If for any reason you require a copy of a recording contact by any means the Stoneacre Compliance Department, Omega Boulevard, Capitol Park, Thorne, DN8 5TX; concerns@stoneacre.co.uk. In order to comply with the Data Protection Act we will require 3 forms of identification.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>11. Finance</p>
<p>Subject to Your status, if after signing the Purchase Order You sign a Finance Agreement with a Finance Company in relation to the Vehicle, the terms of the Finance Agreement will replace this Supplier Agreement. The standard terms of the Finance Agreement will be stated on the Finance Agreement form that You will be asked to sign.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Decidebloom Ltd t/a Stoneacre, Omega Boulevard, Capitol Park, Thorne, DN8 5TX, is authorised and regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority. Our FCA number is 308726. You can verify this by visiting the FCA website or by contacting the FCA on 0854 606 9966.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>12. Complaints</p>
<p>In the event of a complaint or dispute of any kind our complaints handling procedure which can be found on our website and is also available from us on request. Where your complaint cannot be resolved, once you have exhausted our internal process please refer to the website for our ADR process.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>13. Unresolved Complaints</p>
<p>Where any dispute cannot be resolved through ADR, this Purchase Order and Contract shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of England and Wales and shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the English Courts.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>All car data is supplied by third-party sources. While every effort is made to ensure the data is as accurate as possible, any inaccuracies are not under our control. Please check with the dealer to confirm specification beforehand.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>MPG (Combined) figures are obtained from laboratory testing and intended for comparisons between vehicles. They are unlikely to represent real world efficiency.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3><strong>Additional Offers</strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>0% Finance as per Stoneacre plan ask staff for details</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>1000 miles free fuel based on combined fuel consumption of the purchased model, available on all New/Used econetic models purchased</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>3 Years Free Servicing based on 12500miles per annum on all New/Used Fiesta Titanium</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Cash Back available subject to Using Stoneacre Finance Plan (Subject to Status)</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Lifeline Guarantee available to purchase on All new and Used Cars</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3><strong>Stoneacre All-Inclusive</strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>(a) 500 excess applies to all policies.</p>
<p>(b) In the event of a fault claim and/or motoring convictions during your policy period, additional premiums may apply.</p>
<p>(c) Examples shown are for drivers aged 25 and over. Other offers available for drivers under 25.</p>
<p>(d) Drivers must have a clean driving licence (minor convictions may be accepted - up to 6 points with a maximum of 3 points per conviction)</p>
<p>(e) A full UK Licence must be held for a minimum of 3 years.</p>
<p>(f) You must hold at least 3 years no claims bonus.</p>
<p>(g) No more than 1 fault claims/accident in the last 3 years.</p>
<p>(h) You must not have any Criminal convictions.</p>
<p>(i) This offer applies to used vehicles up to the value of 15,995.</p>
<p>(j) Named drivers may be accepted but will be subject to additional criteria.</p>
<p>(k) High-performance vehicles are excluded from this offer.</p>
<p>(l) This free insurance is specific only to the policyholder named at the time of purchase.</p>
<p>(m) Additional costs will be charged directly to the consumer if any material alterations are made to the policy. Changes to the policy remain the responsibility of the policyholder and Brinsworth Insurance and will not form part of the existing financial agreement with Stoneacre.</p>
<p>(n) If vehicle ownership changes the insurance contract will be void from the date of the ownership change.</p>
<p>(o) The insurance is non-transferrable.</p>
<p>(p) We will contact you every year to ensure the policy still meets your requirements. We will require your authorisation to renew the policy each year.</p>
<p>(q) If documentation is not received your policy may be cancelled.</p>
<p>(r) Certain postcode areas may be excluded.</p>
<p>(s) Certain occupations may be excluded.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3><strong>Stoneacre Price Promise</strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Deal to be based on an identical car (age, mileage, colour, make, model and after car purchase from Stoneacre, Price Promise based on an identical car (age, mileage, colour, make, model and condition) at a competitor franchise dealer. Quote needs to be valid within 7 days. Ask for details. Excludes new and pre-registered vehicles.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3><strong>Ex Rental/Lease Cars</strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>A selection of our pre-owned vehicles may have had multi-users previously.</p>
<h3></h3>
<h3><strong>Group SMS Campaigns</strong></h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Terms and conditions apply to all our group SMS campaigns, each campaign may include offers that are exclusive to that particular location and may not be available at other Stoneacre dealerships. Full terms and conditions are available at the participating site, ask for details.</p>
</div>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>

<section class="section-wrapper ">
<section class="section-wrapper-inner grid-x text-center bgwhite block-card-container">
<section class="grid-x large-12 medium-12 small-12 grid-margin-x flex-child-auto content-block">
<section class="cell grid-x large-12 medium-12 small-12 flex-flip">
<section class="large-6 medium-12 small-12 copy flex-child-auto">
<div>
<p>Our constant aim is to make your car buying experience, service visit and any other interaction with Stoneacre a memorable one - for all the right reasons. We pride ourselves on delivering exceptional levels of customer service and after sales support, and we work hard to enhance each customer experience by developing long lasting relationships.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Although our intention is to provide a level of service that meets and exceeds each customers' expectations, we recognise that on occasion things might not go quite to plan. If this happens, we welcome any feedback you may have, along with information regarding the details of any ongoing concern.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Please use the form below provide these details and to let us know where we could have done better. You can see our full <a href="https://www.stoneacre.co.uk/concerns-procedure" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><strong><u>complaints procedure</u></strong></a>.</p>

					<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Stoneacre Complaints procedure]]></title>
		<link>https://stoneacre.anvil-designs.co.uk/stoneacre-complaints-procedure/</link>
		<pubDate>Mon, 07 Jun 2021 01:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://stoneacre.anvil-designs.co.uk/?page_id=181</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[[et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" background_color="#41A02D" custom_padding="0px||0px|||"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"]<h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">Stoneacre Complaints Procedure<br /></span></h1>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" type="4_4"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"]<section class="pagebuilder-container pagebuilder">
<section class="section-wrapper ">
<section class="section-wrapper-inner grid-x text-center bgwhite block-card-container">
<section class="grid-x large-12 medium-12 small-12 grid-margin-x flex-child-auto content-block">
<section class="cell grid-x large-12 medium-12 small-12 flex-flip">
<section class="large-6 medium-12 small-12 copy flex-child-auto">
<div>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Stoneacre Motor Group - Customer Relations Handling Policy</strong></h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">
<p style="text-align: center;">Stoneacre Motor Group recognises that customer concerns offer us as a business the opportunity to correct problems.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">In addition, they frequently provide us with constructive ideas for improving the customer experience, adapting our marketing practices, upgrading services, or modifying promotional materials.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">We understand that, however comprehensive our customer commitment and support packages are, that from time to time, with the very mechanical nature of cars, that unavoidable problems will arise, that rightly leads to consumer complaints. However, learning to recover and address any issues can transform potentially angry or dissatisfied customers into loyal ones.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Analysing our complaints and complaint trends informs Stoneacre Motor Group how we can do our job better by alerting management to the problems that need our prompt attention and correction. Furthermore, they provide long-range opportunities for product innovation and problem prevention.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Stoneacre Motor Groups Complaints and Consumer Support Policy has been formulated in conjunction with Doncaster Trading Standards Service and forms part of our Assured Trader Scheme, the Complaints Policy has been designed to provide consumers with confidence with our advertising, sales, servicing and after-sales processes and provides a guarantee to our customers that Stoneacre Motor Group operates to the highest levels of legal compliance in relation to trading standards legislation and customer services.</p>
</div>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" border_color_all="#41A02D" border_width_all="25px" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"][et_pb_column _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" type="4_4"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"]<section class="pagebuilder-container pagebuilder">
<section class="section-wrapper background bggrey">
<section class="section-wrapper-inner grid-x text-center bgwhite block-card-container">
<section class="grid-x large-12 medium-12 small-12 grid-margin-x flex-child-auto content-block">
<section class="cell grid-x large-12 medium-12 small-12 flex-flip">
<section class="large-6 medium-12 small-12 copy flex-child-auto">
<div>
<h3 style="text-align: center;"><strong>How to make your complaint</strong></h3>
<p style="text-align: center;">In the first instance please contact either the person with whom you have been dealing with or the General Manager of the dealership. You can do this by either telephoning, writing or by email (contact details are provided below)</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">You may also choose to contact the Stoneacre Customer Relations Team directly. However, we would suggest in the majority of circumstances your complaint can be easily resolved at the dealership level.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Contact: customer.relations@stoneacre.co.uk</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">A record of the nature of your complaint will be made, including contact details. Where possible, the person you have been dealing with or the General Manager will take steps to resolve your complaint (Depending on the nature of the complaint, it is not always possible for the person you have been dealing with or the General Manager to be in a position to resolve your complaint).</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">After a period of no longer than 48 hours after the receipt of your complaint, if your complaint has not been resolved you will be contacted and advised that the complaint has been unable to be resolved and that it is being referred to the Stoneacre Customer Relations Team.</p>
</div>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" type="4_4"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"]<p style="text-align: center;">After referral to the Stoneacre Customer Relations Team the representative will have a period of eight weeks to work with you to endeavour to resolve your complaint satisfactorily.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">The Customer Relations team have a maximum of eight weeks to resolve your complaint, but will endeavour to reach agreement with you as soon as possible. If it becomes apparent that an agreement will not be reached or the eight weeks has lapsed and your complaint remains unresolved, a representative of the team will contact you to advise you that this is the case. It may be that in certain circumstances, with your agreement, that the complaint may still easily be resolved but that the resolution cannot be achieved within the time limit. If this is the case and you are agreeable the Customer Relations Team will advise you in writing of a date before which your complaint will be resolved.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Where after the eight weeks following the referral of your complaint to the Customer Relations Team or if it becomes apparent that an agreement will not be reached and your complaint remains unresolved and no agreement on a resolution and time scale have been agreed, the Customer RelationsTeam will refer your complaint to Doncaster Trading Standards Service for adjudication.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Stoneacre Motor Group provides Alternative Dispute Resolution in conjunction with South Yorkshire Trading Standards Services who are accredited by the Chartered Trading Standards Institute under The Alternative Dispute Resolution for Consumer Disputes (Competent Authorities and Information) Regulations 2015.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">On receipt of the complaint referral to Doncaster Trading Standards an impartial investigation will be conducted to consider any relevant evidence provided by either the consumer or the Customer Relations Team. Under certain circumstances the investigating officer may require the provision of additional information and hold discussions with either party. Where no resolution has been reached within a period of 7 days the investigating officer will make written recommendations, details of which will be provided to both parties.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Any recommendation will be binding on Stoneacre Motor Group but will not preclude the consumer from seeking redress or satisfaction through the courts.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Consumers may at any time seek advice from any third party including by contacting the Citizens Advice consumer helpline on:</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">08454 04 05 06</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" custom_padding="11px|||||" custom_margin="-13px|auto||auto||"][et_pb_column _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" type="4_4"][et_pb_button button_text="Contact Us" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" button_alignment="center" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]]]></content:encoded>

					<item>
		<title><![CDATA[Gender Pay Gap]]></title>
		<link>https://stoneacre.anvil-designs.co.uk/gender-pay-gap/</link>
		<pubDate>Mon, 07 Jun 2021 01:17:10 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://stoneacre.anvil-designs.co.uk/?page_id=185</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[[et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" background_color="#41A02D" custom_padding="0px||0px|||"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"]<h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">Gender Pay Gap<br /></span></h1>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" type="4_4"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"]<section class="pagebuilder-container pagebuilder">
<section class="section-wrapper ">
<section class="section-wrapper-inner grid-x text-center bgwhite block-card-container">
<section class="grid-x large-12 medium-12 small-12 grid-margin-x flex-child-auto content-block">
<section class="cell grid-x large-12 medium-12 small-12 flex-flip">
<section class="large-6 medium-12 small-12 copy flex-child-auto">
<div>
<p style="text-align: center;">Decidebloom Limited is required by law to publish an annual gender pay gap report.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">This is a report for the snapshot date of 5th April 2018.</p>
<section class="pagebuilder-container pagebuilder">
<section class="section-wrapper ">
<section class="section-wrapper-inner grid-x text-center bgwhite block-card-container">
<section class="grid-x large-12 medium-12 small-12 grid-margin-x flex-child-auto content-block">
<section class="cell grid-x large-12 medium-12 small-12 flex-flip">
<section class="large-6 medium-12 small-12 copy flex-child-auto">
<div>
<p style="text-align: center;">- The mean gender pay gap is 35%</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> - The median gender pay gap is 22%</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> - The mean gender bonus gap is 77%</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"> - The median gender bonus gap is 76%</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">- The proportion of male employees receiving a bonus is 82% and proportion of female employees receiving a bonus is 58%</p>
</div>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</div>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>
</section>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" background_color="#41A02D" custom_padding="0px||0px|||"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column type="4_4" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"]<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">Pay Quartiles by Gender</span></h2>
<h1 style="text-align: center;"></h1>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_row _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" type="4_4"][et_pb_accordion _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0" closed_toggle_background_color="#FFFFFF" open_toggle_background_color="#41A02D" open_toggle_text_color="#000000" toggle_text_color="#000000" toggle_level="h3"][et_pb_accordion_item title="Band A " _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" open="off" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"]<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">Males: 63%</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">Females: 37%</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">Includes all employees whose standard hourly rate places them at or below the lower quartile</span></p>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="Band B" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" open="on" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0"]<div data-tab-content="" class="accordion-content" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="e4r3cr-accordion-label" aria-hidden="false" id="e4r3cr-accordion" style="display: block;">
<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">Males: 59%</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">Females: 41%</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">Includes all employees whose standard hourly rate places them above the lower quartile but at or below the median</span></p>
</div>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="Band C" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0" open="off"]<div data-tab-content="" class="accordion-content" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="6ejudw-accordion-label" aria-hidden="false" id="6ejudw-accordion" style="display: block;">
<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">Males: 80%</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">Females: 20%</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">Includes all employees whose standard hourly rate places them above the median but at or below the upper quartile</span></p>
</div>[/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title="Band D" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" hover_enabled="0" sticky_enabled="0" open="off"]<div data-tab-content="" class="accordion-content" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="0h9gkz-accordion-label" aria-hidden="false" id="0h9gkz-accordion" style="display: block;">
<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">Males: 91%</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">Females: 9%</span></p>
<p><span style="color: #ffffff;">Includes all employees whose standard hourly rate places them above the upper quartile</span></p>
</div>[/et_pb_accordion_item][/et_pb_accordion][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section]]]></content:encoded>

<p>We employ over 1,100 members of staff at our factory. Over 15,000 vehicles are produced each year in one of the caravan and motorhome industrys largest production sites in Europe.</p>
<p>State-of-the-art machinery and technology guarantee maximum efficiency and the utmost precision. 		<content:encoded><![CDATA[[et_pb_section fb_built="1" fullwidth="on" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_fullwidth_slider _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" custom_padding="250px||250px|||"][et_pb_slide _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" background_enable_color="off" background_image="https://stoneacre.anvil-designs.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/Header_Image-Beachy-1.png" background_enable_image="on" sticky_transition="on"][/et_pb_slide][/et_pb_fullwidth_slider][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_row column_structure="1_2,1_2" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_image src="https://stoneacre.anvil-designs.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/2022_ww_beachy_420_mood_sitzen_heck_drinnen_people_aussen_1448_BEAR_PRESSE_lowres.jpg" title_text="2022_ww_beachy_420_mood_sitzen_heck_drinnen_people_aussen_1448_BEAR_PRESSE_lowres" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" min_height="182.8px" custom_padding="||7px|||"]<h1 class="v1MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><b>THE BEACHY - </b>A BEACH VIBE ON WHEELS</h1>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p class="v1MsoNormal"><b></b></p>
<p class="v1MsoNormal">The BEACHY is a symbiosis of a camper van and Harald Striewskis first home-made Hobby caravan. It is compact and particularly charming with its round shape. One unique gimmick is the large rear door: sitting on the bed and looking at the water gives you a real beachy feeling  whether at the beach, in the mountains or in the city. Born on the beach in northern Germany, the BEACHY is at home anywhere.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built="1" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" custom_margin="-61px|||||" custom_padding="||0px|||"][et_pb_row column_structure="1_2,1_2" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" width="100%" custom_padding="0px||||false|false"][et_pb_column type="1_2" _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default"]<h2 class="v1MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"><strong>Specs</strong></h2>
<p class="v1MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;"></p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version="4.9.4" _module_preset="default" text_font_size="12px"]<table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 199px;" border="1">
